<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Outfit', 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: #FFFBF5; color: #1A1208; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-w: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; }
    .header { margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .logo { width: 50px; height: 50px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E8441A, #F59E0B); border-radius: 12px; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white; font-size: 24px; }
    h1 { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #1A1208; }
    p { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #4A3728; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 14px 28px; background-color: #E8441A; color: white; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; border-radius: 12px; }
    .footer { margin-top: 40px; font-size: 12px; color: #B5957D; }
    .warning { font-size: 14px; color: #B5957D; margin-top: 20px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">🍕</div>
    </div>
    <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    <p>We received a request to reset your password. Click the button below to choose a new one:</p>
    <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="btn">Reset Password</a>
    <p class="warning">If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.</p>
    <div class="footer">
      © {{year}} Slice of Swadesh. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
